{"tid":1955633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北區醫院有病房7名病人確診帶耐多藥鮑氏不動桿菌","createTime":"2020-04-02T15:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T05:10:00.000Z","uid":21255,"like":102,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ba5884dfde58a08de7cde475b6cfa059386cdf","tid":1955633,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"北區醫院發言人表示，一個內科病房上月22日起，先後有7名年齡介乎66歲至95歲的女病人，確診帶有耐多藥鮑氏不動桿菌，正接受隔離治療，4人情況穩定；另外2人及1人因自身疾病，情況分別是嚴重及危殆。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，由於公立醫院已啟動「緊急應變級別」，該病房已全面暫停探訪，已根據既定指引加強執行感染控制措施，包括徹底清潔及消毒相關病房、加強病人及環境篩查，以及嚴格執行接觸傳播防護措施。院方已將個案呈報醫管局總辦事處及衞生防護中心跟進。<br />\n<br />\nburn~~~"},{"pid":"28d09f4ac25e832fa916728097f01e34531ec9f7","tid":1955633,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1b95e794c280f1a80a72072f59541d28450031","tid":1955633,"uid":189109,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"好勁㗎？"},{"pid":"40712cf76d5c52f9a2f1b0bf0f3b36e08e87258c","tid":1955633,"uid":200070,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"fc1b95e794c280f1a80a72072f59541d28450031","tid":1955633,"uid":189109,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"好勁㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"對免疫力差既人長期病患係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84793e43dc07598db15e6244e45728407adc3b44","tid":1955633,"uid":29917,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"帶耐多藥鮑氏不動桿菌"},{"pid":"796